\end_inset

 AARTFAAC All Sky Monitor aims to carry out Image plane transient detection
 in near real-time.
 In this paper, we describe the imaging strategy tailored to satisfy the
 latency constraints of the instruments, under the limited case of detecting
 transients.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Section
List of possible work
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
Effect of different array configurations on the generated images (by looking
 at images sampled closely in time, but with different array configurations).
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
Effect of Imaging parameters on temporal consistency of images.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
Difference imaging: beating the confusion noise limit.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
Searching for transients in the difference image domain.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
Reliability of flux of sources by calibration.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
Stacking of images over a wide bandwidth.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
Temporally integrated images: Working at multiple cadences for the AARTFAAC.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
Image domain effects of the ionosphere, and accounting for them.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
Extracting lightcurves.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
Theoretical parameters of the imaging (Expected noise and sensitivity limit)
 Vs.
 obtained parameters.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
Astrometry: Comparison of the extracted fluxes and positions of sources
 in final images.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
What is the maximum number of pixels we can have, given the sampling of
 our beam?
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
What about multi-frequency synthesis? How can we stack images across the
 band to increase sensitivity?
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
What is the theoretical brightness sensitivity and point source sensitivity
 of the AARTFAAC? How does it influence transient searches? How does it
 compare with actual sensitivities achieved? How does the weighting affect
 this sensitivity? What about the bright sources which are not at the phase
 center? What is the sensitivity theoretically achievable for them?
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
Note that the SNR of a detection depends on the kind of weighting chosen,
 so what is appropriate for AARTFAAC?
\end_layout

